title: #92Noon! Wolves Win, Wild Lose/Lavelle/Tom Chorske
description: PA is joined by Brianne of House Toddler, in for Nordo as producer for most of the week. The Wild lost, the Wolves won. Lavelle E. Neal III Opals in from Florida, ahead of Twins Training Camp. Embarrassing school sports tales.  And Tom 'Hockey Logic' Chorske joins in studio to discuss the remainder of the Wild's season.
